    "description": "Adani Enterprises is actively seeking a talented and motivated Production Engineer to join our dynamic team in Visakhapatnam. This is an excellent opportunity for professionals who are passionate about making a real impact in a fast-growing organization.\n\nAbout Adani Enterprises:\nAdani Enterprises is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Ensure product quality meets internal and customer specifications\n• Conduct root cause analysis for quality rejections and defects\n• Oversee daily production operations to meet output targets\n• Implement lean manufacturing and continuous improvement initiatives\n• Manage raw material procurement and inventory levels\n• Train and supervise shop floor workers and supervisors\n• Ensure environmental compliance and waste management\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Post Graduate Diploma in relevant field\n• 12-20 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in SolidWorks\n• Proficiency in PPAP\n• Proficiency in SAP MM/PP\n• Proficiency in Supply Chain Management\n• Proficiency in Quality Control\n• Proficiency in ISO 9001\n• Proficiency in TPM\n• Proficiency in Statistical Process Control\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Meal coupons and food allowance\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Referral bonus program\n• Annual performance appraisal\n• Salary Range: 35 LPA - 70 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Visakhapatnam, Andhra Pradesh, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Adani Enterprises!",
